    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Nonces exist to make signatures non-replayable. They need to be discarded once they're used.\r\n\r\nThe problem you describe is real though but it's a limitation of ERC-2612 (the permit spec).\r\n\r\nThere have been [proposals to fix this](https://github.com/amxx/permit#out-of-order-execution) but they should be standardized before being implemented.",
